{"tid":2389493,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《最終幻想7：重製版》製作人：以積極的方式欺騙玩家","createTime":"2021-02-01T03:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T17:51:06.000Z","uid":25345,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"5a4404518126815e42e11bd35e0bcee807a44d15","tid":2389493,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T03:05:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i3.read01.com/SIG=1deiv5j/305432454c416a474b6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi3.read01.com%2FSIG%3D1deiv5j%2F305432454c416a474b6e.jpg&h=cadcb954&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《最終幻想7：重製版》的製作人北瀨佳范和聯合導演濱口直樹近日在電腦娛樂開發者大會（DECED）上接受了一次採訪，他們在採訪中談到了《最終幻想7：重製版》第二部分的創作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他們在採訪中承認了第二部分的敘事結構，並暗示可能會有更多偏離原作故事的內容。 北瀨還強調了顛覆玩家期待的重要性&mdash;&mdash;他的目標是以積極的方式欺騙玩家。 北瀨表示開發團隊在致力於繼續讓《最終幻想7》世界的其他部分都像米德加德那樣細節滿滿，達到「不禁令人驚訝，還超出玩家的期待」的程度。 此外，在團隊的創新部分，濱口稱他們已經經歷了第一部分「動作戰」的戰鬥系統，他們想為這個系統做出更多貢獻。新加入的員工們貢獻了很多不同的想法，希望能讓他們為作戰系統創造出新的驚喜。"},{"pid":"404c85d9d261ca464d9e65156087e151f553f9e7","tid":2389493,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:40:56.000Z","msg":"aerith<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7eaa838aa02a552b3164052df3281f14c1226c7","tid":2389493,"uid":135959,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T05:16:03.000Z","msg":"好驚，想有happy end 但好驚炒晒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"256862a76d5b5d7d6044544cc709c26afff937b5","tid":2389493,"uid":221490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T05:17:24.000Z","msg":"遊戲界都冇限炒冷飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0bb0298d9c5d0558af48c86e2f814228df7aa3","tid":2389493,"uid":221490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"256862a76d5b5d7d6044544cc709c26afff937b5","tid":2389493,"uid":221490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyT